title: OPen Tues 7:45-8pm, High ceiling, H/W Floors (1219 Taylor #10
posting_body: ['1st', 'Floor 2BR/1BA Apartment', '* $3,250/month annual lease', '* Bay windows', '* Modern kitchen', '*', 'Available: Now.', 'OPEN HOUSE: Tuesday(8/2) 7:45pm-8pm', 'Address:1219 Taylor #10', 'Old style San Francisco apartment with a modern touch at the heart of Nob Hill (east-facing side).', 'Classic Edwardian building is a block-and-a-half from Grace Cathedral and Huntington Park.', 'Several MUNI lines and a cable car at your doorstep and an easy walk to Chinatown and the Financial District make the location hard to beat.', 'Grocery stores, laundromats, excellent restaurants and cafes all close by.', 'Walk Score is 97, Transit Score is 100.', 'High ceilings with original detail, hardwood floors except in kitchen and bath, and large windows with energy-efficient double-pane installations will keep the noise out, the heat in, and provide lots of light.', 'Kitchen includes gas stove, dishwasher, microwave and granite counters.', 'Lots of cabinet space.', 'Windows have curtains or blinds.', 'Both front rooms face Taylor Street and get wonderful morning light.', 'Inner bedroom gets mid-day and afternoon light.', 'West-facing kitchen gets afternoon light.', 'Landlord pays for water, heat (steam) and garbage.', 'No pets, no smoking.', 'Street parking only.', "Tenant pays a one-time broker's fee.", 'Everest Mwamba', 'DRE# 01717299', 'Kenney & Everest Real Estate', 'DRE# 01984640', 'show contact info', 'office', 'Apply at: <URL>', 'Leasing and Real Estate: Our Family Business for Over 100 Years.', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
